"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"It feels lonely … to be in the crypto space.\\n\\nI really does. The fact that when people hear you are investing in crypto, and they feel like you are one of the victims of some kind of ponzi schemes. They don’t frequently use the word ‘ponzi’ often now, because in this bull run, defi and NFTs have raised awareness among some traditional players, from the bank, the VCs, to the gaints and retailers. \\n\\nHowever, this is far from being adequate for mainstream adoption. There has to be a moment in the near future that crypto and the real blockchain industry that empowered by cryptos to stand out. A perfect-tailor product that make more people realize that crypto is not a devil, on the contrarary, an angel that can be a cure to some many problems which we are facing today.\\n\\nHope that future is not far beyond.\",\"timestamp\":1640787474,\"title\":\"It's time to become mainstream\"},\"digest\":\"LPQqhA-9q3v0i-dtAQ5pxZBVAiZdyZVTecpBw3NMqX0\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x4A904725eF49f8874cD354E3F609d6696457ED4e\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"GajRj6T9ABsLGQO8eqfYvEU1EK-4Oc4l9Yajwcm1a-s\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Qeknqpytqp8aC-ojQk88eElJY7w_3s-9HZ5YU0llfJ4\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"uyvK9g7D5zKosO12JuoNr1UbXWoROjyMAzWzKzBqvkK39DSxnECopjrh2vYTALSYN7RMhuYpeevCEALQa1j1hw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xd39050aed761e114c811573f566e3bc50b053e4f1c0cfcd1fc2744c6e62e7e273d481072e8b738be026fdf0c4342e33339dfee91961b1a8c88b5a5f1006bc7111c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"GajRj6T9ABsLGQO8eqfYvEU1EK-4Oc4l9Yajwcm1a-s\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Qeknqpytqp8aC-ojQk88eElJY7w_3s-9HZ5YU0llfJ4\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\